            <lg type="edition">
<l>aṟavāḻi yantaṇaṉ ṟāḷcērntārk kallāl</l>
<l> piṟavāḻi nīnta laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>None can swim the sea of vice, but those who are united to the feet of that gracious Being who is a sea of virtue.</l>
